#Football Practice
#Start practice
1. take attendance 
1. line kids up to warm up
1. begin warmups
1. water break

#Practice
1. assign coaches to stations
1. divide number of players in groups
1. insruct players on drill
1. demonstrate drill to players
1. begin drill
1. break for water
1. rotate stations
1. instruct players on drill
1. demonstrate drill to players
1. begin drill
1. break for water
1. rotate stations

#Conditioning
1. designate starting point for kids to line up
1. explain conditioning 
1. designate end point or finish line
1. begin conditioning

#End of Practice
1. acknoweldge hard work
1. designate hard workers of the day
1. break down practice
1. dismiss kids from practice
1. clean up field and put equipment away


